The Collective Digital Studio is building the premier next generation media company, offering premiums online video hits from today&rsquo;s top digital stars.&nbsp; The company is building out a video entertainment platform that enables our millennials audience to find the latest hits and discovery up-and-coming hits, delivers marketers targeted audiences in and around premium content and supports our creators in delivering their videos and building their brands through all forms of digital platforms.</p>
<p>
<br />
About the job:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Develop and improve the front end for our new video platform possible.&nbsp; With the traffic we handle, you will need expert Javascript skills and site optimization experience.</li>
<li>
Participate in architecture discussions, design decisions and provide input into all aspects of the product.</li>
<li>
Research new technologies to improve existing features or create new features.</li>
<li>
Maintain and troubleshoot existing web applications and site functionality (Improve the scalability and performance of our platform).</li>
</ul>
<br />
<p>
About you:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Minimum 5 years experience designing and developing robust and scalable web applications.</li>
<li>
Solid experience in OO JavaScript programming.</li>
<li>
Working knowledge of source control software. (We use Git).</li>
<li>
Recent experience and strong competence in page development using XHTML 1.1, HTML, and CSS3.</li>
<li>
Self-motivated, results oriented, team player and with a passion for his/her work.</li>
<li>
Front-end site optimization experience and strategies.</li>
<li>
Deep understanding of the intricacies of rendering across browsers IE 7+ on Windows, Firefox, Chrome and Safari</li>
<li>
Some experience with Ruby, python or PHP frameworks.</li>
<li>
&nbsp;B.S. in Computer Science or equivalent degree</li>
</ul>
